@node "require" "-System Requirements-"
@toc "main"
GOldNEST is multitasking, you can switch screens with left-amiga + M.
But I don't guarantee that GOldNEST is safe for your system.

 To run GOldNEST, you will (probably) need the following:

   * Kickstart 3.0 or later
   * diskfont.library (V39 or later)
   * asl.library (V39 or later)
   * iff.library (V23 or later, If you want to save iff pics)
   * AGA or GFX-board (Probably)

   * A NES-Rom image to edit would be nice too. =)

@endnode

